EPTRI will NAK host until EP_OUT is primed to receive
EPTRI EP_OUT receives ZLP acknowledgement from host
while the control endoint FIFO has data, read the 8 bytes of the setup packet
Write response data to EP_IN FIFO
Prime EP_IN to transmit FIFO contents
prime EP_OUT to receive ZLP from host
check that the FIFO is empty (zlp)
select the EP_OUT endpoint to prime
